reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This small journal is perfect. Nice leather, stamped tree design so nice. Gives you a 0lace to put date, check off day of week and more.Very nice item and price was good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful leather binding and great for daily journalism!!
reviews.reviewText: I love the soft green leather (green is what I picked). This journal is organized really well. On every page there is a symbol for that day's weather as well as a place to record the date and day of the week. I find these helpful to my memory after surviving a coma and traumatic brain injury. I like the satin strip page keeper so I can go to the latest day that I have recorded. There is also a stretchy keeper with a matching leather tab for closing the entire journal or just any section I might want to keep marked and held securely. This is a beautiful looking and well made journal that you can pick in several different colors of leather binding. What a well thought out tool I can use daily to record my memories. Highly recommend!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice Journal- Great Gift Idea
reviews.reviewText: I needed a gift for my nephew. He writes beautiful poetry. I wanted to encourage him in this, so I bought this journal. It was very well received. The leather exterior is tooled and a gorgeous deep leather brown. The pages are cream colored with lines. The size of the journal is perfect with plenty of pages. The journal is a perfect size for him to tuck into his backpack in college.When my nephew is famous, this journal will be a fine symbol of the quality of written arts he produced in his 18 th year. Looking for a nice gift? This is a very reasonably priced journal with lovely designs and materials from binding to pages.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love these notebooks. I needed something durable and good looking that would not easily lose pages like a spiral notebook. These fit the bill perfectly. The cover material looks and feels nice. The ribbon and retaining strap are nice touches.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Something anyone could appreciate
reviews.reviewText: this journal is much more impressive in person than it was on-line. The cover is cushy, more for use at home than putting in a purse or briefcase, or even an inside jacket pocket. I purchased many of this brand of journal as gifts for the men in my life, but would be perfectly fine for a woman. The pages are thick enough that most inks should not leak through (these are lined pages) there is a book mark and pocket in each one. size is easily manageable and not awkward at all. I will keep this product in mind for future gifts to others, it would be right at home in a welcome to your new home basket with stamps, pens, etc for an economical but necessary housewarming gift. Very pleased with the multitude of colors offered, the quality of the product, the price, the quickness of delivery. I recommend this product highly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One nice journal
reviews.reviewText: The outer cover on this journal is really nice. I am not sure if it's leather, but it has that appearance. The cover is sewn onto the book itself giving this journal a classy look. Each page has a place to put the date, what's happening with the weather and the day of the writing. There are 20 lines per page. I find this journal to be one nice book to journal in. The book is about 1 inch thick, or a little less. It's definitely worth the money I paid.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Well made & I like it so far. Pages are nice, color is bright & page holder seems to be sewed in well.
